title: Practical Electronics for Inventors Third Edition

English | ISBN: 0071771336 | 2013 | 1040 pages | EPUB, MOBI | 82 MB 

THE ELECTRONICS KNOW-HOW YOU NEED TO BECOME A SUCCESSFUL INVENTOR

If there is a successor to Make: Electronics, then I believe it would have to be Practical Electronics for Inventors.

perfect for an electrical engineering student or maybe a high school student with a strong aptitude for electronics.

Ive been anxiously awaiting this update and it was well worth the wait.
